lead_paragraph: SUFFOLK COUNTY FAIR.--The annual Fair of the Suffolk County Agricultural Society took place on Friday at Smithtown. The attendance was unusually large, and the display of stock, agricultural and domestic products and fancy articles, exceeded by far those of any previous year, and was indeed highly creditable to our friends at the east end of Long Island,
